{
  "texts": [
    "The target displacement is extracted using fluoroscopy images.",
    "The robotic manipulator uses the estimated target location to compensate for the respiratory motion by steering a needle attached to its end-effector.",
    "Needle steering preserves the alignment between the needle and the target.",
    "The second step involves the remote teleoperation of the robotic arm.",
    "An end-user uses a haptic device to control the motion of the arm to perform the needle insertion task (Fig. 1)."
  ]
}